DocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uhg1689058930415.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhg1689058930415.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhg1689058930415.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uhg1689058930415\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface Community Edition uses the Sentinel Cloud Server for license management. The\n\t\tUniface Enterprise Edition also supports the Sentinel RMS License Manager (or Server) to\n\t\tenforce and manage licensing in a multi-user environment.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhg1689058930415__p_d140951e1_d140952e1_d140953e1\">Sentinel relies on the\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LM_LICENSE_FILE</span> option or environment variables to locate\n\t\t\tlicenses.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4401522\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4401522\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "License management Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 24, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Uniface Community Edition uses the Sentinel Cloud Server for license management. The Uniface Enterprise Edition also supports the Sentinel RMS License Manager (or Server) to enforce and manage licensing in a multi-user environment. Sentinel relies on the LM_LICENSE_FILE option or environment variables to locate licenses. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}